eq \alpha_2$. We want to show that there is $i \in I$, $Y\in {m Perf}_S$, and a map $ eta: h^{m top}_Y\otimes W_i	o \sff$ such that $\alpha_1 eta 
eq \alpha_2  eta$. Since $\alpha_1
eq \alpha_2$, there exists $Y \in {m Perf}_S$ such that $\alpha_{1,Y}
